==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Castor oil
<hw>Cas"tor oil</hw> <pr>(k⟦acr⟧s"t⟦etil⟧r oil`)</pr>. <def>A mild
cathartic oil, expressed or extracted from the seeds of the <spn>Ricinus
communis</spn>, or <spn>Palma Christi</spn>. When fresh the oil is
inodorous and insipid.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Castor-oil plant</b></col>. <cd>Same as <er>Palma
Christi</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Castrametation</ent>⟦br⟧
